{"tid":2273200,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK「帶妝抱熊貓」氣炸陸網　熊貓研究中心發聲：調查中！","createTime":"2020-11-05T14:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T01:28:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a2e14dd46a07d931f662ad087edb7d1e46d2f8","tid":2273200,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"南韓女團BLACKPINK紅遍全球，每發新歌總會掀起一陣討論潮，只不過最近在團綜《24/365 with Blackpink》裡竟引發了一些爭議，只見4位女孩來到首爾近郊的愛寶樂園，與剛出生100天的熊貓「福寶」見面，卻被發現身上的裝備恐對熊貓有所為害，在陸網引起大批網友討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5251/d5251838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5251%2Fd5251838.jpg&h=204fe22c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK在全球都有超高人氣。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK IG）<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK近日隨著團綜《24/365 with Blackpink》的拍攝，來到愛寶樂園與熊貓寶寶「福寶」見面，幾位女孩開心地抱著熊貓，小心翼翼地呵護著，看起來相當興奮，只不過她們身上僅穿著簡易防護服與口罩，引起了大批大陸網友的不滿，認為她們臉上帶妝，在沒有戴好手套和帽子的情況下觸摸，會增加熊貓感染細菌的風險，恐造成嚴重後果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5251/d5251841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5251%2Fd5251841.jpg&h=5b6194ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK到愛寶樂園見熊貓。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，「福寶」是首隻在南韓誕生的熊貓，她的父母是旅韓熊貓夫婦愛寶、樂寶，從2016年起交流期為15年。根據大陸熊貓外借的相關規定，在海外出生的熊貓仍屬大陸所有，一般在3歲左右就必須返回大陸，且當地有設立法規保護熊貓，不能讓飼養員外的人接觸熊貓，如有非必要接觸，則必須全身配戴正規的防護套裝才可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5251/d5251842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5251%2Fd5251842.jpg&h=d5ee932d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK帶妝抱熊貓，引起大路網友憤怒。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n因此，這一次BLACKPINK沒有穿著整套防護服接觸熊貓，也引起了大陸網友的憤怒，根據《封面新聞》報導，目前大陸大熊貓研究中心已經獲悉此事，表示正在著手調查以及進行處理。"},{"pid":"1de3c88ec33abf537da1c3044b9c0e6aa15805f7","tid":2273200,"uid":337986,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"用大陸法律吿鳩blackpink囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65ca597b064c2b41f90724afbab06c640085253","tid":2273200,"uid":101481,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"外國出世都無用 生生世世都係中國熊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721e67f18b615735e520c87dca0d7d895e41a2d8","tid":2273200,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"嘩好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時學cctoy來我大bp fb派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cfd17c0b7dbdd6985c8e0053016a3e64fecda2","tid":2273200,"uid":368812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK得番BLACK了"},{"pid":"492acab5444bbac435f6db2a134b673ded09cead","tid":2273200,"uid":79427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"外國岀世都無外國身份證？"},{"pid":"a98bf11c78e2de220fcda75a6c469b27ee553d28","tid":2273200,"uid":117516,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"3歲就要番支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfrEzFh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfrEzFh.png&h=e470a60c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb2c8806e2abf8c88a5e1398f1f380bb2424a4e1","tid":2273200,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"little pink 玻璃心到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e15c7ac0e397f7c224960d09d221da88ae36fbc","tid":2273200,"uid":371815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"末撚住